{"tid":449651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美3航母首集結亞太　震懾中朝","createTime":"2017-10-27T11:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T14:50:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"87566ab4cb79e0d7d28ac49c8ae83e7ddeba8d15","tid":449651,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:13:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171027/20196005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20196005&d=ueduJ9UI%2FfU5gbN3igvYfv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=358def29\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171027%2F20196005&h=1971e448\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20171027/20196005</a><br />\n<br />\n美3航母首集結亞太　震懾中朝<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171027/large/a1703a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171027%2Flarge%2Fa1703a.gif&h=b6cf25de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美軍兩個航空母艦戰鬥群近日相繼抵達亞洲太平洋地區，連同目前停泊在日本、剛與南韓完成聯合軍演的「列根號」，共有3艘同時在第七艦隊管轄範圍內。<br />\n<br />\n朝官稱核試非隨便說說<br />\n<br />\n「尼米茲號」核動力航母戰鬥群較早前完成在中東掃蕩「伊斯蘭國」（IS）的支援任務後，啟程回國，已進入印度洋，途中有機會在第七艦隊管轄區域停泊。而剛執行完任務的「羅斯福號」戰鬥群，也於周一到達西太平洋。軍方並未提及3艘航母是否有特定任務。軍事分析員、前海軍上將柯比（John Kirby，圖）認為，中國持續在南海島礁加強軍事建設，美軍想藉此舉帶出「美國仍是太平洋地區最大軍事力量」，同時警告北韓別輕舉妄動。另有分析指，安排3艘航母在同一區域十分罕有，美軍刻意在特朗普訪亞洲前如此部署，明顯是擺出「高姿態」。<br />\n<br />\n另方面，北韓外相李永浩上月指北韓或會在太平洋進行試爆氫彈，惹來外界質疑。北韓外交官李容弼接受美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）訪問時，強調外界應該認真看待有關言論，因李永浩「熟知領袖金正恩的想法」，絕對不是隨便說說。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡"},{"pid":"092a0ce29ba4508f86ef6409de6a7b3952c58360","tid":449651,"uid":40470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"蒙住對眼睇佢唔到就唔會驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c544a0bf298cab220535e8d0bcdbdc8fe6e328","tid":449651,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:23:44.000Z","msg":"將佢改名就唔存在啦"},{"pid":"1598e050114539396719054b7ea3833fa851c133","tid":449651,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"俾我係中國立刻射核彈擊沉對方航母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2071dd59ebc71368ac8ba4169d16030397c4c58c","tid":449651,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"支那狗無聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d4befe2973c5069d771aafbc4e8b37a8bd734c","tid":449651,"uid":11753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蒙住對眼睇佢唔到就唔會驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瞇埋眼當睇唔到咪得"},{"pid":"74e894ee094b73a2e11900d294c48353a7de96e4","tid":449651,"uid":55077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾我係中國立刻射核彈擊沉對方航母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nG持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 東風21"}]}